<devicesets>
<deviceset name="WE-SFIA_2013" prefix="L">
<description>&lt;b&gt;WE-SFIA SMT Flat wire inductor
&lt;br&gt;

&lt;br&gt;Characteristics 
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt; heights (2010, 2013, 2016) for maximum design flexibility
&lt;br&gt;High-current saturation for high ripple applications
&lt;br&gt;Flat wire construction
&lt;br&gt;Very low DC resistance for less heat dissipation
&lt;br&gt;Operating temperature: -40°C to 180°C

&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Applications 
&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Non-isolated switch mode power supply
&lt;br&gt;DC-DC converter
&lt;br&gt;High-current inductor for output filtering
&lt;br&gt;High-end audio power inductor for automotive audio systems
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.we-online.com/components/media/o883493v209%20Family-WE-SFIA-784364210033-784364210082-784364210360.jpg" title="Enlarge picture"&gt;
&lt;img src="https://www.we-online.com/components/media/o883493v209%20Family-WE-SFIA-784364210033-784364210082-784364210360.jpg" width="320"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;p&gt;
Details see: &lt;a href="www.we-online.com/catalog/WE-SFIA/?utm_source=eagle_model&amp;utm_medium=description_link&amp;utm_campaign=eisos_eagle"&gt;www.we-online.com/components/products/WE-SFIA&lt;/a&gt;&lt;p&gt;

Updated by Ella Wu 2026-02-25 &lt;br&gt;
2026 (C) Würth Elektronik</description>
